quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Father of the flame of a smokeless fire`s (known as Prophet Mohammad`s uncle) hand was destroyed/lost, and destroyed/lost"
  111,2,His property/possession/wealth and what he gained/acquired did not enrich/suffice from him
  111,3,He will roast/suffer/burn (in) a fire that of (a) flame of smokeless fire
  111,4,And his woman (wife) the fire wood`s/fuel`s carrier/lifter
  111,5,In her neck/beautiful neck (is a) rope from palm fiber tightly woven rope/an iron ring